name: The Bali Major
description: Bali Major is the third major of the 2022 - 2023 Dota 2 Pro Circuit that will be held at one of the most attractive tourist destination in the world Bali, Indonesia. The tournament features 18 teams that will be competing from 29th June - 9th July for the huge prizepool of 500,000 USD and 3500 DPC points.
